file: tmp_【 3DLIVE 】ねね～ちらい～ぶ４年目もよろしくね！ゲストいっぱいでお祝い！【 #桃鈴ねねの４年目 】 [5Ney9Z_WnTU]_gemini-3-flash-preview/reencoded/part_001.mov

scenes.description: Momosuzu Nene performs her original song 'Momonone', but stops halfway due to a mistake.
A transition sequence showing various illustrations of Momosuzu Nene and other Hololive members.
Momosuzu Nene restarts the performance of 'Momonone' from the beginning.

subtitles.original:
モモノネ
作詞・作曲・編曲：ヒゲドライバー
subtitles.english:
Momonone
Lyrics, Composition, Arrangement: Hige Driver

subtitles.original: いくつもの　夢という花が
subtitles.english: Several flowers called dreams

subtitles.original: この惑星(ほし)　には咲いていたんだ
subtitles.english: Were blooming on this planet

subtitles.original: 自分も　手にとって憧れては
subtitles.english: I too, picked them up and yearned for them

subtitles.original: 思い切り　羽を広げたんだ
subtitles.english: And spread my wings as wide as I could

subtitles.original: みんな見えるかー？
subtitles.english: Can everyone see me?

subtitles.original: そう　不安な時も
subtitles.english: Yes, even in uneasy times

subtitles.original: あ、あ、みんなバイバイ！ちょっと待って、やり直し！ごめんねー！
subtitles.english: Ah, ah, bye-bye everyone! Wait a second, redo! Sorry!

subtitles.original: あー、みんなー！あ、いいえ、みんな何も見てなかった、いいね？
subtitles.english: Ah, everyone! Ah, no, everyone saw nothing, okay?

subtitles.original: もう一回、最初から、始めよう！
subtitles.english: One more time, from the beginning, let's start!

subtitles.original: イエーイ！
subtitles.english: Yay!

subtitles.original: あ、今度こそねねがどこにいるかわかりましたかー？
subtitles.english: Ah, this time, did you find where Nene is?

subtitles.original: わー！見える見える！
subtitles.english: Wow! I see you, I see you!

subtitles.original: いくつもの　夢という花が
subtitles.english: Several flowers called dreams

subtitles.original: この惑星(ほし)　には咲いていたんだ
subtitles.english: Were blooming on this planet

subtitles.original: 自分も　手にとって憧れては
subtitles.english: I too, picked them up and yearned for them

subtitles.original: 思い切り　羽を広げたんだ
subtitles.english: And spread my wings as wide as I could

subtitles.original: そう　不安な時も
subtitles.english: Yes, even in uneasy times

subtitles.original: いつも支えてくれてるねっこ
subtitles.english: The Nekko who are always supporting me

subtitles.original: だからきっと　もっと大きくなれる
subtitles.english: So surely, I can grow even bigger

subtitles.original: 思いはまっすぐ　伸びていけ
subtitles.english: May my thoughts stretch out straight

subtitles.original: あの空に　届くように
subtitles.english: To reach that sky

subtitles.original: モモノネ　なんて...
subtitles.english: Momonone is...
